text: Chantal Laboureur (born 4 January 1990 in Friedrichshafen) is a German beach volleyball player. ==Professional career== Since 2015 her teammate has been Julia Sude. ==World tour 2016== At the 2016 Grand Slam at Long Beach, California, In semi final action (Aug 27, 2016) Laboureur and Julia Sude lost to Kerri Walsh Jennings and April Ross of United States straight sets (21 - 17, 21 - 16). Bronze medal match (Germany vs Germany) the pair won in straight sets (21-16, 21-17) against Katrin Holtwick and Ilka Semmler.http://worldtour.2016.fivb.com/en/316/women/standingshttp://www.fivb.org/EN/BeachVolleyball/Competitions/WorldTour/2016/event/Results.asp?TournCode=WLOB2016&Phase;=2 The pair competed at the Toronto World Tour finals in Sept. 2016 placing 1st in Pool D and advance to Quarter Finals. == References == ==External links== * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:German women's beach volleyball players Category:People from Friedrichshafen Category:Sportspeople from Stuttgart Category:Universiade medalists in beach volleyball Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Germany Category:Medalists at the 2013 Summer Universiade
